	  <concept id="i1123082"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">4.404</ph> Contract clause.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d211e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d213e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1063713.dita#i1063713"
                        base="i1063713"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.204-2</xref>, Security Requirements, in solicitations and contracts when the contract may require access to classified information, unless the conditions specified in <ph class="- topic/ph ">paragraph (d) of this section</ph> apply.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d213e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            If a cost contract (see <xref href="FAR-i1104678.dita#i1104678"
                        base="i1104678"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">16.302</xref>) for research and development with an educational institution is contemplated, the contracting officer shall use the clause with its Alternate I.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d213e44" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            If a construction or architect-engineer contract where employee identification is required for security reasons is contemplated, the contracting officer shall use the clause with its Alternate II.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d213e53" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            If the contracting agency is not covered by the NISP and has prescribed a clause and alternates that are substantially the same as those at <xref href="FAR-i1063713.dita#i1063713"
                        base="i1063713"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.204-2</xref>, the contracting officer shall use the agency-prescribed clause as required by agency procedures.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
